entries.femaleVariant: Stanley here with ya, and we got another day ahead of us in this city of dreams.
Oo, I love this town! Love it like you might love a mother who popped you out on the steps of an orphanage once and now stops you to ask if you got a smoke for her!
Every new day here means a hundred new arrivals! But only half these gonks’ll survive a year. And that’s if it’s a good one!
And why do these peeps come to NC? Well, to be street samurai like Morgan Blackhand and Weyland Boa Boa! The greater the risk, the bigger the bounty, kids. Or so they say…
But you can only be a major league player for so long. The faster you live, the faster you burn out – if you don't get a bullet to the brain first!
NC's legends! Know where you’ll find most of ‘em?!
Matters not where you’re from, matters not where you start.
What matters here is the walk you walk.
